{"tid":1111972,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【降魔的2.0】馬國明：感情上有新突破","createTime":"2019-04-17T07:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T15:50:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75b13f0d73724583b5ecf7b1eec27ce5458fc36c","tid":1111972,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2473137/org/b3a6e68be8b4c1a051e63eed28e362b3.jpg/2xP_swmc0gpgWl6MlEyt_51aIqn4jY9_zn97Vc5_e1U?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2473137%2Forg%2Fb3a6e68be8b4c1a051e63eed28e362b3.jpg%2F2xP_swmc0gpgWl6MlEyt_51aIqn4jY9_zn97Vc5_e1U%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=deb68259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上一輯《降魔的》黃智雯（飾莊芷若）是馬國明（飾小馬）的女神，兩人的感情線會在新的一輯會延續落去。馬明話：「其實上一輯芷若唔記得鬼域嘅時間，到呢一輯會令到佢有返啲記憶，佢會記返起同小馬經歷過一啲嘢，咁所以我同佢會有一啲突破，芷若喺呢一輯會有啲奇遇，會遇到一啲靈界嘅嘢，今次黃智雯冇做魔嘅角色，純粹係做返芷若嘅角色，佢會多啲參與靈界嘅事。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2473174/org/765f0dfa08fb5fe31e051120bedf0d31.jpg/eAvUV-ofVrP8bOF903geXwrgNGOQ_TGdr2_NBolvzQY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2473174%2Forg%2F765f0dfa08fb5fe31e051120bedf0d31.jpg%2FeAvUV-ofVrP8bOF903geXwrgNGOQ_TGdr2_NBolvzQY&h=cdbe148c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/298454/%E9%99%8D%E9%AD%94%E7%9A%842-0-%E8%8A%B7%E8%8B%A5%E8%88%87%E5%B0%8F%E9%A6%AC%E6%9C%83%E9%96%8B%E8%8A%B1%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C-%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%8E-%E6%84%9F%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%89%E6%96%B0%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4#media_id=2473174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F298454%2F%25E9%2599%258D%25E9%25AD%2594%25E7%259A%25842-0-%25E8%258A%25B7%25E8%258B%25A5%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%259E%259C-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2598%258E-%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%25A0%25B4%23media_id%3D2473174&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=d25f1834\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/298454/%E9%99%8D%E9%AD%94%E7%9A%842-0-%E8%8A%B7%E8%8B%A5%E8%88%87%E5%B0%8F%E9%A6%AC%E6%9C%83%E9%96%8B%E8%8A%B1%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C-%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%8E-%E6%84%9F%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%89%E6%96%B0%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4#media_id=2473174</a>"},{"pid":"97aa62d4cb0eb42f9d02cc038b31bf60e19b58ae","tid":1111972,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"車窗都關上了 載走的過客有多少<br />\n倒鏡影照面具 蓋住或是獸與妖<br />\n終點都不見了 要怎超脫世態紛擾<br />\n刧數可有預兆 何時被愛呼召<br />\n<br />\n誰願見死不救 滴水不漏 像一顆石頭<br />\n能同渡多少春與秋 一千歲亦自覺不夠<br />\n無懼我心傷透 蕩揮衣袖 萬般帶不走<br />\n無論是快樂與難受 也只不過剎那感受<br />\n<br />\n應知花花世界 妄想一剎那已走歪<br />\n志氣可以賤賣 每步陷阱任你踩<br />\n光陰走得太快 重傷一次你會長大<br />\n到處天闊地大 誰評定我好壞<br />\n<br />\n誰願見死不救 滴水不漏 像一顆石頭<br />\n能同渡多少春與秋 一千歲亦自覺不夠<br />\n無懼我心傷透 蕩揮衣袖 萬般帶不走<br />\n無論是快樂與難受 也只不過剎那感受<br />\n<br />\n愛得深厚 受傷之後 亦都想逗留<br />\n能同渡多少春與秋 一千歲亦自覺不夠<br />\n無懼我心傷透 蕩揮衣袖 萬般帶不走<br />\n凡塵沒有甚麼永久 樂與苦不惦掛身後 暢遊"},{"pid":"10a5d304c22cb9fe2638e88277f23eba8561d671","tid":1111972,"uid":99700,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"黃智雯正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bf3736041b9edcf15cacac929b66a9b81044ea","tid":1111972,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370cf38bede1f5fcc602422a71df1bd777163f85","tid":1111972,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:46:50.000Z","msg":"慘<br />\n開工仲要對住架的士"},{"pid":"eead129f9e4aa5ea8d8fab61269e1168d08d6aa3","tid":1111972,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislik